data.description: Welcome to this RARE 3bd/2ba manufactured home with an oversized 1-car attached garage! You don't see these often. As you walk in the inviting red front door, you will immediately see the endless opportunities available with the garage and extra storage space! Once you step in the front door of the home, you'll enjoy the cozy setting of the open floor plan including living room and kitchen with an eating area in the main area. This home has a split floor plan with a primary bedroom and an ensuite bathroom on one side of the home, separated from the other two bedrooms on the other side of the home. This way everyone gets a little more privacy. Each bedroom also has it's own closet and is steps away from the second full bath for ease. A great patio off the kitchen will allow you to take a step outside to relax or take in the mature trees that surround the home. The backyard is an open opportunity for it's future family; previously a fabulous space used for outdoor gardening, the backyard also features a large shed for extra storage and is partially fenced. The home and yard has been known to have several friendly wildlife visitors, such as deer, pay it a regular visit! Come take a tour of this great home!
